title: Nicki Minaj Releases “Queens Got Da Crown” Playlist on TIDAL
text:
Home > Music > Nicki Minaj Releases “Queens Got Da Crown” Playlist on TIDAL Nicki Minaj Releases “Queens Got Da Crown” Playlist on TIDAL 0 0 Posted by Danny Schwartz  29pm Listen to Nicki Minaj's 35-track playlist of all Queens artists for TIDAl. 
Earlier today , Nicki Minaj revealed that she had created something "super dope" for TIDAL. As it turns out it's not a song or a video; it's a playlist. 
"Queens Got Da Crown" is a 35-track playlist curated by Nicki Minaj that features songs by Queens artists. Not surprisingly, it begins with the three songs she released Thursday night, then continues with a selection of tracks by Queens greats like Nas, 50 Cent and G-Unit , Ja Rule , N.O.R.E., Mobb Deep , Lost Boyz, LL Cool J , Q-Tip , and Run-DMC. It is her second playlist in two days, following yesterday's release of her "Pretty Girls Like Trap Music" playlist with 2 Chainz . 
Listen to "Queens Got Da Crown" below.
